abstract_str: ian lam , 42 , plunged 60ft to his death on saturday from top of a car park . crowd gathered below and some people yelled : ` get on with it and jump ' he fell to ground and was pronounced dead at the scene by medics . his family released a statement expressing their ` overwhelming loss ' described him as a ` kind , caring and loving man ' and asked for privacy . west mercia police condemned ` appalling ' actions of the taunting crowd .
